flexibility of our algorithm in practice,\nwhich is resilient to both oblivious and adaptive jamming attacks with\ndifferent intelligence and any attacking strength that ranges from no-attack to\nthe full-attack of all spectrum resources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 May 2015 12:28:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 May 2015 12:44:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2015 14:22:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2015 09:07:34 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2015 07:44:34 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2015 04:26:24 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2015 06:54:17 GMT"},{"version":"v8","created":"Sat, 30 Jan 2016 06:33:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
